speech.p: I have written to the Secretary of State about Kirkstall Forge railway station in my constituency. It opened just over a year ago, but only one train stops there an hour. If we are going to open new railway stations, we must have trains stopping at them. Will he agree to meet Arriva Rail North to talk about the frequency of services at Kirkstall Forge, so that we can get maximum benefit out of this housing and business development?
